OL,3,CFirst Minister finds balance in son's
OL,4,Chockey ahead of budget
OL,6,FScotland's First Minister has spoken
OL,7,Fof the "balance" he found in taking
OL,8,Fhis son to hockey training the night
OL,9,Fbefore his first budget in charge.
OL,11,FJohn Swinney took over the top job
OL,12,Funexpectedly earlier this year after
OL,13,Fthe resignation of Humza Yousaf, which
OL,14,Fcapped off a calamitous 12 months for
OL,15,Fthe SNP.
OL,17,FMr Swinney returned after a year-long
OL,18,F"sabbatical" ` as he describes it `
OL,19,Ffollowing his nine-year tenure as
OL,20,Fdeputy first minister to Nicola
OL,21,FSturgeon.
