OL,3,CFirst Minister finds balance in son's
OL,4,Chockey ahead of budget
OL,6,FIn the early weeks of his tenure the
OL,7,FFirst Minister stressed the importance
OL,8,Fof finding time to spend with his
OL,9,Fteenage son and wife Elizabeth.
OL,11,FSpeaking to the PA news agency, Mr
OL,12,FSwinney said it had been "challenging"
OL,13,Fto maintain some semblance of a home
OL,14,Flife while also being the country's
OL,15,Ftop politician, particularly recently,
OL,16,Fwith the Scottish Government
OL,17,Fpublishing his first budget since
OL,18,Ftaking the top job.
OL,26,@tD@ZOUtD@fO]
