OL,3,CFirst Minister finds balance in son's
OL,4,Chockey ahead of budget
OL,6,F"I've had a very demanding week ` I
OL,7,Fhave a demanding week every week, but
OL,8,Fthis is a particularly demanding
OL,9,Fweek," he said.
OL,11,F"So I stood to be away from home for a
OL,12,Fvery protracted amount of time, but I
OL,13,Fmanaged to get home on Tuesday and
OL,14,Fthen the minute I got home, I took
OL,15,FMatthew to his hockey practice."
