OL,3,CFirst Minister finds balance in son's
OL,4,Chockey ahead of budget
OL,6,FHe added: "For me to get home and take
OL,7,Fhim to hockey, I came back into work
OL,8,Fon Wednesday morning for budget day
OL,9,Ffeeling as if I had got the balance
OL,10,Fright and the balance was taking my
OL,11,Fson to hockey ` so that made me feel
OL,12,Fvery at ease."
OL,14,FHis ascension to the top job has also
OL,15,Fseen his family caught in the middle
OL,16,Fof tense political moments.
