OL,3,CFirst Minister finds balance in son's
OL,4,Chockey ahead of budget
OL,6,FHe spoke a week after the First
OL,7,FMinister was subjected to abuse from
OL,8,Fthe crowd at the memorial service for
OL,9,FAlex Salmond at St Giles Cathedral in
OL,10,FEdinburgh as he arrived with his wife.
OL,12,FSome in the waiting crowd booed the
OL,13,FFirst Minister, with shouts of
OL,14,F"traitor" also aimed at him as he
OL,15,Fhelped Elizabeth ` who has mobility
OL,16,Fissues caused by multiple sclerosis `
OL,17,Finto the venue.
