OL,3,CFirst Minister finds balance in son's
OL,4,Chockey ahead of budget
OL,6,FMr Swinney ` ever reticent to be too
OL,7,Fopen about his personal life ` said:
OL,8,F"I don't think that kind of behaviours
OL,9,Freally is for that occasion, but it's
OL,10,Fwater off a duck's back for me."
OL,12,FAsked how his wife ` an accomplished
OL,13,Fformer BBC political journalist ` had
OL,14,Fhandled it, Mr Swinney said: "As an
OL,15,Fexperienced, formidable political
OL,16,Fjournalist who I'm very pleased is no
OL,17,Flonger asking me questions on camera,
OL,18,Fmy wife's well versed in politics."
